Document: WebSocketMultiplayerPeer
Path: godot/classes/class_websocketmultiplayerpeer.rst
Summary: Implements the MultiplayerAPI interface using WebSocket.

WebSocketMultiplayerPeer is a low-level implementation of the MultiplayerAPI interface that uses WebSocket for network communication. It allows you to send and receive data over a WebSocket connection, making it suitable for real-time multiplayer games and applications.

Inherits: PacketPeerExtension < PacketPeer < RefCounted
